      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TA IN ADVANCE (10) has recorded two wins and two minor placings from the past five starts. Didn't let supporters down at his latest appearance when he got the job done by 2 metres over 2130m at Gloucester Park. May just need a bit of luck at some point from this difficult draw. Finds a suitable assignment and will be a major force once more. ESCAPEFROMREALITY (8) could only manage third last start over 2242m at Narrogin, beaten 6 metres, after a win at the previous appearance over 2242m at Narrogin. May need luck at some stage extracting from the inside of the second row. Finds a suitable assignment and can return to winning form. NEVERTELLMETHEODDS (4) finished fourth two runs ago then broke and finished a distant seventh over 2223m at Narrogin at the latest appearance. Facing a tougher assignment but a big run is possible if his race manners improve. HOT ROD (5) is worth plenty of thought off a last-start win by 1.1 metres at Narrogin over 2242m.",
